high_descs: move forward across the room towards the stove and turn right at the stove
move to the counter where the toaster is and pick up the spatula off of the counter
move the spatula towards the back of the counter
put the spatula on to the plate at the back of the counter
pick up the plate with the spatula on it
turn right and move towards the sink and face the sink
put the plate with the spatula on it into the sink
anns.task_desc: put and plate with a spatula into the sink

high_descs: Move to stand at the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the spatula from the counter in front of the toaster.
Move closer to the counter while holding the spatula.
Place the spatula on the round pan to the right of the toaster.
Pick up the pan with the spatula on it from the counter.
Carry the pan and spatula to the kitchen sink.
Place the pan and spatula in the right side of the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a spatula and pan to the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Walk to the stove, turn right
Walk to the counter
Take the spatula from the counter, put it on the plate
Turn to the right
Head to the sink
Turn to the left
Put the plate in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the spatula on the plate, put the plate in the sink
